es.codeurjc - package es.codeurjc
This is the main package of the project which contains the Application class that runs the Spring Boot Application.
es.codeurjc.classes - package es.codeurjc.classes
This subpackage contains Java classes used in the web application, such as: User - All about user info and data.
es.codeurjc.controllers - package es.codeurjc.controllers
This subpackage contains all Controllers used in the web application, such as: AuthController - Controls the mapping of auth page which contains all the requests related to log in and register.
es.codeurjc.services - package es.codeurjc.services
This subpackage contains all Services used in the web application, such as: AuthService - Service that manage all about authenticate and serves the process of login and register of someone inside the Web Application SecurityService - Service that manage all about security
